data.eml:eml: New genus and species names for the Eocene lizard Cadurcogekko rugosus Augé, 2005

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Bolet, Arnau, Daza, Juan D., Augé, Marc, Bauer, Aaron M. (2015): New genus and species names for the Eocene lizard Cadurcogekko rugosus Augé, 2005. Zootaxa 3985 (2): 265-274, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3985.2.5
